description:
15 minutes away from Central Park

2 over-sized bedrooms, with queen sized beds, walk-in closets (so stay for a little or for awhile!), and over-sized windows
Bedrooms come with large dressers and art decorum
PLENTY of natural fresh light
Bathroom
Raindrop shower head
Chef Kitchen
Sub-zero commercial refrigerator
Viking commercial stove
Great work space and open area connected to kitchen
Features a large coat closet
2 large futons and additional art decor
Washer and Dryer located ON SITE

hosts.about: Love incredible food and trying out as many places around NY as possible. Passion for fishing, art, and checking out new spots around all the boroughs on my Vespa (don't hate).

house_rules:
• Check in time is flexible
• No smoking
